    },
    {
      "id": "boss_raid_rule_popup_desc_10001",
      "content": "- \"Reflectrial][lairtcelfeR\" is a <color=#ff0000>high-difficulty challenge</color>.\nLevel up and Uptie/Threadspin your Identities and E.G.O to <color=#ff0000>meet the recommended specs</color> before entering the battle.\n(※ Support Identities cannot be used.)\n\n- Each boss battle features unique effects.\n\"Shade of Reflection\" effects apply on all difficulties.\n<color=#f8c200>\"Tribulation\" effects apply on Hard Difficulty only.</color>\n\n- Reflectrial][lairtcelfeR battles <color=#f8c200>allow a maximum of 3 Team Loadouts</color> to be used in order.\nHowever, Identities assigned to a previous loadout cannot be reused in subsequent Loadouts.\n\n- <color=#f8c200>A 12-turn limit</color> is applied to each Team Loadout.\nExceeding 12 turns or opting to end the battle on your current loadout will save the state of battle progression (Boss Unit's Combat Phase, HP, and SP; as well as E.G.O Resources owned). You may continue progressing through the battle with the next loadout.'\n(※ The Boss unit's pattern, the non-Boss enemies' HP and SP, and status effects on enemies are not saved)\n\n- Starting from the second Loadout, <color=#f8c200>the starting SP of your team increases</color> upon entering the battle, based on the cumulative Turn count (※ 5 per turn).\n\nMinus Coin Identities start with negative SP numbers instead (※ -5 per turn, min -25)."
    },
